result.calculatedFormula:
IF(AND(ISBLANK(KLWSpec__c), NOT (ISBLANK(Drawing__c))),
	CASE(TEXT(Order.Region__c),
		'3', Drawing__r.DrawingBase__r.Product__r.NameRUS__c + ' ' + Drawing__r.AxLoadType__r.Name + ' (' + Drawing__r.Name + ')',
		'19', Drawing__r.DrawingBase__r.Product__r.NameRUS__c + ' ' + Drawing__r.AxLoadType__r.Name + ' (' + Drawing__r.Name + ')',
		'13', Drawing__r.DrawingBase__r.Product__r.NameUKR__c + ' ' + Drawing__r.AxLoadType__r.Name + ' (' + Drawing__r.Name + ')',
		Drawing__r.DrawingBase__r.Product__r.Name + ' ' + Drawing__r.AxLoadType__r.Name + ' (' + Drawing__r.Name + ')'
	),
	IF(AND(NOT (ISBLANK(KLWSpec__c)), ISBLANK(Drawing__c)),
		CASE(TEXT(Order.Region__c),
			'3', KLWSpec__r.SpecBase__r.ProductType__r.NameRUS__c + ' ('+ KLWSpec__r.Name + ')',
			'19', KLWSpec__r.SpecBase__r.ProductType__r.NameRUS__c +  ' ('+ KLWSpec__r.Name + ')',
			'13', KLWSpec__r.SpecBase__r.ProductType__r.NameUKR__c +  ' ('+ KLWSpec__r.Name + ')',
			KLWSpec__r.SpecBase__r.ProductType__r.Name + ' ('+ KLWSpec__r.Name + ')'
		),
		IF(AND(ISBLANK(KLWSpec__c), ISBLANK(Drawing__c)), Product2.ProductKind__r.Name + ' ' + WheelSteelGrade__r.Name + ' ' + WheelProductStandard__r.Name, 
			IF(AND(NOT (ISBLANK(KLWSpec__c)), NOT (ISBLANK(Drawing__c))),
				CASE(TEXT(Order.Region__c),
					'3', KLWSpec__r.SpecBase__r.ProductType__r.NameRUS__c + ' ' + Drawing__r.AxLoadType__r.Name + ' ('+ KLWSpec__r.Name +' / ' + Drawing__r.Name + ')',
					'19', KLWSpec__r.SpecBase__r.ProductType__r.NameRUS__c + ' ' + Drawing__r.AxLoadType__r.Name + ' ('+ KLWSpec__r.Name +' / ' + Drawing__r.Name + ')',
					'13', KLWSpec__r.SpecBase__r.ProductType__r.NameUKR__c + ' ' + Drawing__r.AxLoadType__r.Name + ' ('+ KLWSpec__r.Name +' / ' + Drawing__r.Name + ')',
					KLWSpec__r.SpecBase__r.ProductType__r.Name + ' ' + Drawing__r.AxLoadType__r.Name + ' ('+ KLWSpec__r.Name +' / ' + Drawing__r.Name + ')'
				), ''
			)
		)
	)
)

result.calculatedFormula:
IF(
  AND(
    NOT(ISBLANK(Drawing__c)),
    NOT(ISBLANK(Drawing__r.WeightKG__c))
  ),
  ShippedQuantity__c * 1000 / Drawing__r.WeightKG__c,
  IF(
    AND(
      NOT(ISBLANK(KLWSpec__c)),
      NOT(ISBLANK(KLWSpec__r.WeightKG__c))
    ),
    ShippedQuantity__c * 1000 / KLWSpec__r.WeightKG__c,
    IF(
      NOT(ISBLANK(Quantity_pcs__c)),
      ShippedQuantity__c / (Quantity / Quantity_pcs__c),
      IF(
        NOT(ISBLANK(Quantity_m__c)),
        ShippedQuantity__c / (Quantity / Quantity_m__c),
        IF(
          NOT(ISBLANK(Quantity_ft__c)),
          ShippedQuantity__c / (Quantity / Quantity_ft__c),
          0
        )
      )
    )
  )
)
result.label: DeliveredQuantity (pcs)
